Written by: Billy Preston & Bruce Fisher

Produced by: Billy Preston

South African record label (unless otherwise stated): A&M

Annual ranking:

Other chart success:

The song would give Preston his first solo number 1 in the US. He would see 1 further US chart topper in the form of 1974’s ‘Nothing From Nothing’. He had seen a US number 1 hit before where he got a separate credit on The Beatles’ 1969 hit ‘Get Back’. In 2009 Donny Osmond included a cover of ‘Will It Go Round In Circles’ on his ‘Love Songs Of The 70’s’ album.
